                            <comment id="17241588" author="kgyrtkirk" created="Tue, 1 Dec 2020 14:51:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;apparently similar things may happen at 2 places:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;metastore might bump into issues adding the same partition for a table&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;during filemove operations issues might happen&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;addressed them both separately&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;because other apis may also use the metastore api - I&apos;ve added a some simple table level locking to the metastore side&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;the filemove operation(s) from now will acquire a SEMI_SHARED lock for the actual table while the file move happens - this will lock out multiple writers from the same partition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</comment>
